    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Partner Game\r\n\r\nFind out what others think of your songs! \r\n\r\n**Round One**\r\n- Find a partner that chose the same GIF as you. \r\n- Take turns playing each other each backtrack and sound effect until you both have played all three. \r\n- Discuss ways to make your songs better, then make changes to your code. \r\n\r\n**Round Two**\r\n- Find a partner who has a different GIF than you. \r\n- Take turns pressing \"Run\" and performing you song. \r\n- Just play one song for them. \r\n- Gather feedback, make tweaks, then find another partner!\r\n- Keep repeating this until you run out of time. \r\n",
